message:
Just a quick re-upload of the Refined Character Creator, for posterity and exposure: perchance.org/ai-character-chat?data=Refined_Character_Creator~c011a2ebf90777702a3dc092326cad47.gz

Makes a character from as little or as much info as you provide, and has a format that is easy to read and edit. 

And the link to the shared character gallery: perchance.org/shared-characters-from-ai-character-chat-comments
